566
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,980
All the pressure is on Jingshu.

567
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:42,060
I'm the one who is unfair to her.

568
00:22:42,870 --> 00:22:44,390
I'm just a man who relied on a woman.

569
00:22:44,670 --> 00:22:46,350
Dumbbell, don't say this.

570
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:48,500
Your priority

571
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:50,460
is to graduate from adult education now

572
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:51,840
and get your coaching certificate.

573
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:53,080
Once you become a private coach,

574
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:55,080
I'm sure you'll make more money
than me, right?

575
00:22:55,080 --> 00:22:56,350
I'll rely on you in the future.

576
00:22:56,430 --> 00:22:57,670
You are so nice, Jingshu.

577
00:22:59,670 --> 00:23:00,500
I'm telling you.

578
00:23:00,630 --> 00:23:01,830
Once I graduate,

579
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,120
I will find a job at a gym.

580
00:23:03,120 --> 00:23:05,350
After working for two years
and gathering some customers,

581
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:07,110
I will establish my own gym.

582
00:23:07,740 --> 00:23:08,830
Then, Jingshu

583
00:23:08,870 --> 00:23:10,540
won't have to sell cars anymore.

584
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,680
Come to the gym
and become the female owner

585
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,740
while nurturing our child.

586
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:14,830
What?

587
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:16,460
Nurturing your child?

588
00:23:16,670 --> 00:23:19,190
You have such a long-term plan.

589
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,080
Anyway, our goal

590
00:23:20,080 --> 00:23:22,390
is to save enough money
to get married within a year.

591
00:23:22,540 --> 00:23:23,540
This time next year,

592
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:25,120
we'll invite you to our wedding banquet.

593
00:23:25,950 --> 00:23:27,080
Let's have a toast then.

594
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:27,880
- Come on.
- Come on.

595
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,150
Congratulations on your marriage.

596
00:23:29,150 --> 00:23:30,110
Stay harmonious forever.

597
00:23:30,110 --> 00:23:31,110
Thank you, both of you.

598
00:23:31,300 --> 00:23:32,110
- Thank you.
- Here.

599
00:23:32,120 --> 00:23:33,600
When are both of you getting married?

600
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:35,350
Us?

601
00:23:35,740 --> 00:23:36,390
I...

602
00:23:36,830 --> 00:23:38,110
Let's get married together.

603
00:23:38,110 --> 00:23:38,920
I have the same idea.

604
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,280
- All right.
- That's the way to go.

605
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:40,720
That works.

606
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,360
Next year.

607
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:41,700
When?

608
00:23:41,910 --> 00:23:42,950
February.

609
00:23:42,950 --> 00:23:43,440
That's good.

610
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:45,000
I will wear the wedding dress with Daji.

611
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,590
Hold on.

612
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,500
All of you, hold on.

613
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:47,740
Did I agree?

614
00:23:47,740 --> 00:23:48,950
Did I say yes?

615
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,950
Daji has something to say.

616
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:54,720
Didn't you say you'll only get married
after you've established your career?

617
00:23:54,780 --> 00:23:55,780
When did I say that?

618
00:23:56,060 --> 00:23:56,830
Just now.

619
00:23:56,980 --> 00:23:58,500
Two hours ago when we were eating.

620
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:02,220
What do you think?

621
00:24:02,430 --> 00:24:04,700
When are you two getting married?

622
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:09,870
We...

623
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:14,300
We plan to establish our careers first

624
00:24:14,630 --> 00:24:15,740
before getting married.

625
00:24:17,020 --> 00:24:17,590
Yes.

626
00:24:23,390 --> 00:24:24,190
Zhou Shui.

627
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:26,190
Look.

628
00:24:26,220 --> 00:24:28,260
Dai Daji is very pretty.

629
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:29,150
Not at all.

630
00:24:29,150 --> 00:24:30,390
She's also talented.

631
00:24:31,300 --> 00:24:33,590
She still doesn't get it
because she's still young.

632
00:24:33,740 --> 00:24:34,780
Can you

633
00:24:35,670 --> 00:24:36,910
get married

634
00:24:36,910 --> 00:24:38,190
before she gets it?

635
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,390
Otherwise, when you think

636
00:24:39,390 --> 00:24:40,630
you're a match for her,

637
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:42,980
you'll be at my age.

638
00:24:47,150 --> 00:24:48,110
It's all nonsense.

639
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:49,950
It's a joyful meal today.

640
00:24:50,540 --> 00:24:51,780
Real emotions and real stories.

641
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:53,020
They are all real.

642
00:24:58,950 --> 00:25:00,830
When do you plan to get married then?

643
00:25:00,950 --> 00:25:02,430
I haven't considered this yet.

644
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:05,260
We'll discuss it in the future.
There's no rush.

645
00:25:05,950 --> 00:25:06,830
Tell me.

646
00:25:06,830 --> 00:25:08,320
What else do you want? I'll work hard.

647
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:09,910
No. You've worked hard enough.

648
00:25:09,910 --> 00:25:10,910
It's not your problem.

649
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:12,870
It's me.

650
00:25:13,190 --> 00:25:13,910
I'm thinking

651
00:25:13,910 --> 00:25:16,540
if there's anything
that requires me to work hard.

652
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:19,980
Hello, Zhaoyang.

653
00:25:20,020 --> 00:25:22,390
Director Zhou is really talented.

654
00:25:22,460 --> 00:25:24,870
You should know how troublesome
my boss is.

655
00:25:24,870 --> 00:25:26,950
When Director Zhou
told my boss about the proposal,

656
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:28,460
we agreed to do it immediately.

657
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:29,630
Lai, I'm telling you.

658
00:25:29,630 --> 00:25:31,830
You must let him stay by your side.

659
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:33,700
Sure. If you need anything,
just call me anytime.

660
00:25:34,150 --> 00:25:35,220
Sure. Bye.

661
00:25:36,460 --> 00:25:38,020
Everyone is praising you.

662
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:39,630
My judgment was right.

663
00:25:39,630 --> 00:25:40,500
Thank you, Zhaoyang.

664
00:25:40,500 --> 00:25:41,670
I will do my best.

665
00:25:42,220 --> 00:25:42,980
Go back to work.

666
00:25:47,700 --> 00:25:48,390
Daji.

667
00:25:48,870 --> 00:25:50,460
Come here. I have something to tell you.

668
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:51,520
Sure.

669
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:53,110
All right.
I'll go and do the storyboard.

670
00:25:53,110 --> 00:25:53,390
Go on.

671
00:25:55,950 --> 00:25:56,540
Zhaoyang.

672
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:57,670
What are your orders?

673
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,540
It's nothing much.

674
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:00,540
I just want to ask

675
00:26:00,780 --> 00:26:02,910
how you feel working at my company.

676
00:26:03,150 --> 00:26:03,950
Are you happy?

677
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:05,910
Yes.

678
00:26:07,060 --> 00:26:08,500
Both of us are satisfied.

679
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:09,830
This is the best job

680
00:26:09,830 --> 00:26:11,300
we've worked.

681
00:26:11,300 --> 00:26:12,280
You treat us too well.

682
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:13,440
Don't see me as your superior.

683
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:15,080
I don't see you
as my subordinate as well.

684
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:15,350
We are

685
00:26:15,350 --> 00:26:17,190
all partners
who started this company together.

686
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:18,440
We can be frank with each other.

687
00:26:18,460 --> 00:26:20,390
But I really don't have anything to say.

688
00:26:20,390 --> 00:26:23,060
I think you are not happy
with your current situation.

689
00:26:28,540 --> 00:26:29,910
I... I'm not.

690
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:33,190
I signed Zhou Shui as a director

691
00:26:33,590 --> 00:26:35,740
but you still don't have
a clear position.

692
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:36,870
Don't you think

693
00:26:36,870 --> 00:26:38,910
this arrangement is unfair to you?

694
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:42,500
I don't think it's unfair.

695
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:44,060
However,

696
00:26:44,780 --> 00:26:46,950
I do feel like doing more things.

697
00:26:48,540 --> 00:26:51,220
Zhou Shui has been telling me
that he wants to film a movie.

698
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:54,020
What about you?
Do you want to film a movie too?

699
00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:11,950
I do.

700
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:16,780
Mr. Hong.

701
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:18,300
This is nothing serious.

702
00:27:18,350 --> 00:27:19,740
Why do you come here on purpose?

703
00:27:20,220 --> 00:27:22,150
We can just release a statement.

704
00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:23,840
We've drafted the statement.

705
00:27:23,840 --> 00:27:25,480
It'll be released
at nine tomorrow morning.

706
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,520
You just need to share it.

707
00:27:26,740 --> 00:27:28,060
Sure. I'll do that.

708
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:30,390
Besides sharing the post,
you need to promise me

709
00:27:30,430 --> 00:27:31,390
three things.

710
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,060
Go ahead.

711
00:27:34,020 --> 00:27:34,700
One.

712
00:27:34,910 --> 00:27:36,300
The statement will clearly state

713
00:27:36,390 --> 00:27:38,830
that you and Chenxing only have
a working relationship.

714
00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:41,700
Everything was taken out of context
by the paparazzi.

715
00:27:42,670 --> 00:27:44,300
Find a few reputable media outlets

716
00:27:44,350 --> 00:27:45,500
to help us share this news.

717
00:27:46,460 --> 00:27:47,500
Sure. No problem.

718
00:27:47,700 --> 00:27:49,220
I can still do this.

719
00:27:49,500 --> 00:27:50,110
Two.

720
00:27:50,300 --> 00:27:53,830
I don't care what relationship
you had with Chenxing previously

721
00:27:53,950 --> 00:27:55,300
but from now on,

722
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:57,460
you will not have
any relationship with him.

723
00:28:01,630 --> 00:28:02,440
He wants to break up?

724
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:06,040
He doesn't even have the guts
to tell me himself

725
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:07,500
and asked you to deliver his message?

726
00:28:07,500 --> 00:28:08,150
Three.

727
00:28:09,430 --> 00:28:11,780
Leave this project that he is filming.

728
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:13,390
You will never appear in any projects

729
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:14,350
related to him.

730
00:28:24,150 --> 00:28:25,590
This request is too much.

731
00:28:27,430 --> 00:28:28,590
Don't you understand?

732
00:28:28,670 --> 00:28:30,220
Chenxing is an idol.

733
00:28:30,500 --> 00:28:32,110
An idol cannot be in a relationship

734
00:28:32,670 --> 00:28:35,110
let alone dating the producer of a film
that he is shooting.

735
00:28:36,060 --> 00:28:37,460
In the future, you must

736
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:39,110
never be seen together.

737
00:28:39,260 --> 00:28:41,220
Not even your names.

738
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:49,390
Mr. Hong.

739
00:28:50,430 --> 00:28:52,980
I created this project alone.

740
00:28:53,780 --> 00:28:56,110
From the script to investment
to getting Yuan onboard.

741
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:57,980
I settled everything myself.

742
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:00,150
This is my project.

743
00:29:00,590 --> 00:29:01,980
I'll never give up on it.

744
00:29:02,430 --> 00:29:03,300
I'll be blunt.

745
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:04,390
One of you must go

746
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:06,950
in this project.

747
00:29:13,190 --> 00:29:14,260
Are you threatening me?

748
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:15,110
Yes.

749
00:29:15,870 --> 00:29:16,950
Don't forget.

750
00:29:17,060 --> 00:29:18,590
I'm also an investor in the film.

751
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:20,150
I can threaten you.

752
00:29:27,280 --> 00:29:28,670
If he wants to leave, let him leave.

753
00:29:29,190 --> 00:29:30,740
Mr. Hong can just pull out if he wants.

754
00:29:30,780 --> 00:29:32,190
I don't need his money.

755
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,220
Mr. Zhang.

756
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:36,150
If Mr. Hong
pulls out from the investment,

757
00:29:36,430 --> 00:29:38,190
it will put
other investors in doubt as well.

758
00:29:38,740 --> 00:29:40,430
Just let all of them leave.

759
00:29:41,630 --> 00:29:43,110
I can mortgage a few of my houses.

760
00:29:44,150 --> 00:29:44,830
Dai.

761
00:29:44,830 --> 00:29:46,110
Ignore them.

762
00:29:46,390 --> 00:29:47,780
I have money. Don't be afraid.

763
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:49,260
It's not about money.

764
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:51,000
If Mr. Hong pulls out
from the investment,

765
00:29:51,220 --> 00:29:52,350
Yuan will leave as well.

766
00:29:52,590 --> 00:29:53,740
Both of them are friends.

767
00:29:54,390 --> 00:29:56,350
Moreover, Lin Chenxing cannot leave.

768
00:29:56,630 --> 00:29:58,700
He is a top-tier star after all.

769
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:01,830
This is about the company's future.

770
00:30:01,830 --> 00:30:02,540
Then...

771
00:30:02,540 --> 00:30:03,350
What should we do?

772
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:04,300
Are you leaving?

773
00:30:04,300 --> 00:30:06,110
Why should I leave my own project?

774
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:07,540
I have a good idea.

775
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:10,260
Why don't you
just make the relationship public?

776
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,880
How can you
let that jerk take advantage?

777
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,150
Not with Lin Chenxing, of course.

778
00:30:13,670 --> 00:30:15,630
With me. We'll be together

779
00:30:15,910 --> 00:30:16,870
and kick him out.

780
00:30:17,300 --> 00:30:19,950
He is just a buddy of yours.

781
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:20,910
What do you think?

782
00:30:20,950 --> 00:30:21,830
You don't say.

783
00:30:22,980 --> 00:30:23,980
It's not bad.

784
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:25,150
Go away.

785
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:26,260
Don't cause trouble, Kid.

786
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:30,980
Dai.

787
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:34,910
You have been too stressed recently.
Go home and rest for a few days.

788
00:30:35,220 --> 00:30:36,950
Leave this to me.

789
00:30:37,590 --> 00:30:38,630
Lin Chenxing,

790
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:39,430
right?

791
00:30:40,320 --> 00:30:41,700
I'll find someone to deal with him.

792
00:30:41,830 --> 00:30:42,910
Stop it.

793
00:30:42,910 --> 00:30:45,020
You're always dealing with people.

794
00:30:47,670 --> 00:30:48,670
I do have an idea.

795
00:30:48,670 --> 00:30:49,910
Go out first.

796
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:51,110
Let me talk to Mr. Zhang alone.

797
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:52,150
Sure.

798
00:30:52,150 --> 00:30:52,540
All right.

799
00:30:52,540 --> 00:30:53,060
Let's go.

800
00:31:01,540 --> 00:31:03,870
Mr. Hong insists on me leaving the project

801
00:31:03,870 --> 00:31:05,500
because he is worried
about my relationship

802
00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:06,430
with Lin Chenxing.

803
00:31:06,910 --> 00:31:08,060
I've thought of something

804
00:31:08,060 --> 00:31:09,460
to make him be at ease completely.

805
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:11,500
However,

806
00:31:13,060 --> 00:31:14,500
I need you to help me out.

807
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:18,110
Have you heard?

808
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:20,150
Zhaoyang is participating
in the Berlin Film Festival.

809
00:31:20,460 --> 00:31:21,220
Berlin?

810
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,300
Isn't that in Germany?

811
00:31:22,300 --> 00:31:23,630
Yes. It's in Germany.

812
00:31:23,700 --> 00:31:25,500
Moreover, I heard rumors

813
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:26,540
that Zhaoyang

814
00:31:26,540 --> 00:31:28,110
was going
to bring someone else with him.

815
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:29,950
Berlin Film Festival?

816
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:32,120
Isn't this an advertising agency?

817
00:31:32,120 --> 00:31:33,800
Why are we participating
in a film festival?

818
00:31:34,150 --> 00:31:35,220
You know nothing.

819
00:31:35,350 --> 00:31:36,980
Zhaoyang came from Shendu Pictures.

820
00:31:36,980 --> 00:31:38,630
He has to return to his roots in film.

821
00:31:38,630 --> 00:31:39,350
He is going there

822
00:31:39,350 --> 00:31:40,590
to know more people

823
00:31:40,670 --> 00:31:42,220
and expand our company's influence.

824
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:44,460
I hope Zhaoyang can bring me with him.

825
00:31:44,460 --> 00:31:45,950
I don't care about films.

826
00:31:45,950 --> 00:31:47,390
I just want to see a few stars.

827
00:31:47,390 --> 00:31:48,670
You're just an accountant.

828
00:31:48,670 --> 00:31:50,020
What are you thinking about?

829
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:51,780
Who is Zhaoyang bringing?

830
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:54,060
Do you even need to ask?
I'm sure he's bringing Zhou Shui.

831
00:31:54,190 --> 00:31:55,040
Is that so, Zhou Shui?

832
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:56,680
I've been interested
in a handbag recently.

833
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,870
Can you bring it back for me?

834
00:31:58,260 --> 00:31:59,590
Zhaoyang hasn't decided yet.

835
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:00,500
Take a look.

836
00:32:00,540 --> 00:32:01,350
This watch as well.

837
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:01,830
Sure.

838
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:03,280
Some of them are...

839
00:32:03,280 --> 00:32:04,640
I don't know where they sell them.

840
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:06,600
Zhou Shui, Daji.
Come to the meeting room with me.

841
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:07,590
He's calling for you.

842
00:32:07,590 --> 00:32:08,110
Go on.

843
00:32:10,120 --> 00:32:11,460
Remember to bring it back for us.

844
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:12,320
I'm going there first.

845
00:32:17,020 --> 00:32:18,430
Don't bring handbags for them.

846
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:20,910
Do you think

847
00:32:20,910 --> 00:32:22,500
Zhaoyang is
really bringing me to Berlin?

848
00:32:22,520 --> 00:32:25,000
I haven't travelled abroad before.
I'm feeling a little nervous.

849
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:26,190
Can you be a little ambitious?

850
00:32:26,950 --> 00:32:27,390
Zhou Shui.

851
00:32:27,390 --> 00:32:28,110
Zhaoyang.

852
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:30,040
How's the new video?

853
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:31,110
It's coming along well.

854
00:32:31,190 --> 00:32:32,910
You must submit it
before Chinese New Year.

855
00:32:32,910 --> 00:32:33,910
Before Chinese New Year?

856
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:36,700
Isn't the Berlin Film Festival
happening during that period?

857
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:37,460
Yes. What about it?

858
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:39,110
How can I film it

859
00:32:39,110 --> 00:32:40,220
if I'm in Europe?

860
00:32:40,500 --> 00:32:41,500
Why are you in Europe?

861
00:32:42,980 --> 00:32:44,760
I'm going with you
to the Berlin Film Festival.

862
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:47,590
You know about it?

863
00:32:48,150 --> 00:32:48,950
It's like this.

864
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:51,220
You are the company's only director.

865
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:53,220
I'm sure you know
how urgent this job is.

866
00:32:53,360 --> 00:32:54,760
There's no need for you to go there.

867
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:56,670
Help me out
and complete the video for me.

868
00:32:57,150 --> 00:32:57,590
Daji.

869
00:32:57,830 --> 00:32:58,870
Come with me this time.

870
00:32:59,110 --> 00:33:00,830
Get prepared.

871
00:33:00,980 --> 00:33:03,260
Give your passport to the admin

872
00:33:03,260 --> 00:33:04,390
so your visa can be applied.

873
00:33:04,430 --> 00:33:05,220
No. I...

874
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:06,350
Am I going with you?

875
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:07,950
What? Do you have other plans?

876
00:33:09,430 --> 00:33:10,700
I don't.

877
00:33:11,190 --> 00:33:11,870
Zhou Shui.

878
00:33:12,060 --> 00:33:13,240
I'm leaving the video to you.

879
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:13,670
All right?

880
00:33:13,670 --> 00:33:13,980
Sure.

881
00:33:13,980 --> 00:33:14,700
Go back to work.

882
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:15,670
I have to talk to Daji.

883
00:33:15,670 --> 00:33:17,880
Sure. I was halfway through the editing.

884
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:21,800
He seems a little stressed.

885
00:33:22,540 --> 00:33:23,740
Have a chat with him later.

886
00:33:23,740 --> 00:33:24,680
Don't let him overthink.

887
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:27,220
Daji, I'm depending on you as well.

888
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:28,830
You know my level of English.

889
00:33:29,060 --> 00:33:30,980
Use your advantage, all right?

890
00:33:31,540 --> 00:33:33,670
Are you just looking for a translator?

891
00:33:34,110 --> 00:33:35,220
Not just a translator.

892
00:33:35,350 --> 00:33:36,190
In every aspect,

893
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,350
including meetings...

894
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:59,390
Let's go and eat.

895
00:34:01,630 --> 00:34:02,670
Let me finish editing this.

896
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:05,590
I'm not hungry. Go on without me.
I'll go and look for you later.

897
00:34:05,830 --> 00:34:06,830
Do it later.

898
00:34:06,830 --> 00:34:08,180
Let's go and eat first.

899
00:34:08,350 --> 00:34:09,620
I'm not hungry.

900
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:10,950
Go ahead.

901
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:12,950
Go on. I'll go and find you later.

902
00:34:14,310 --> 00:34:17,270
Zhaoyang told me
he asked me to go with him

903
00:34:17,270 --> 00:34:18,980
because he thinks I'm good at English

904
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:20,540
so I can become his translator.

905
00:34:20,950 --> 00:34:22,310
He is just trying to save money.

906
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:24,620
Actually, we're just going

907
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:27,310
to talk about business
and advertisements.

908
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:29,060
There aren't any movie projects.

909
00:34:30,180 --> 00:34:31,920
When you make a blockbuster film
in the future

910
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:34,000
and we participate
in the film festival with the movie,

911
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:35,280
it'll make everyone proud, right?

912
00:34:35,540 --> 00:34:36,870
Are you comforting me?

913
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:38,540
Yes.

914
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:40,460
I'm not angry.

915
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,230
I think it's a good thing
for you to go there.

916
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:43,960
It's the same
no matter which of us is going.

917
00:34:44,660 --> 00:34:45,980
Why aren't you eating then?

918
00:34:46,060 --> 00:34:47,020
I'm not hungry.

919
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:48,230
Moreover, I must submit this.

920
00:34:49,270 --> 00:34:49,950
All right?

921
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:52,270
Go on. I'll look for you later.

922
00:34:52,710 --> 00:34:53,390
Go on.

923
00:34:54,180 --> 00:34:55,620
- All right.
- I'll be done soon.

924
00:34:57,710 --> 00:35:00,120
I'll give you the mission
of bringing back handbags for them.

925
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:01,430
I won't be doing that.

926
00:35:10,180 --> 00:35:10,520
Come on.

927
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,200
- It's all right.
- Let me carry it.

928
00:35:12,270 --> 00:35:13,430
I can't let my boss do this.

929
00:35:13,950 --> 00:35:14,950
It's fine.

930
00:35:14,950 --> 00:35:15,750
Let me do it.

931
00:35:16,460 --> 00:35:17,180
Daji!

932
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:20,310
Zhou Shui is here.

933
00:35:20,310 --> 00:35:21,600
Let me talk to him for a while.

934
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:22,950
Sure. I'll get in the car first.

935
00:35:22,950 --> 00:35:23,800
What are you doing?

936
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,910
Why are you here?
You didn't wear a jacket.

937
00:35:25,910 --> 00:35:26,710
Here. Take this.

938
00:35:26,870 --> 00:35:27,540
Do you feel cold?

939
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:27,950
No.

940
00:35:28,060 --> 00:35:28,720
What is this?

941
00:35:28,720 --> 00:35:31,360
Let's not be stingy since this is
your first time traveling abroad.

942
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:33,720
I took out all my salary
and changed it into Euros for you.

943
00:35:33,720 --> 00:35:34,310
- No need.
- Go.

944
00:35:34,710 --> 00:35:36,960
- I won't spend any money.
- It's your first time traveling.

945
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:37,720
We can't be stingy.

946
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:39,230
I'm not. I won't spend any money.

947
00:35:39,790 --> 00:35:40,750
Zhaoyang, thanks.

948
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:42,060
Don't catch a cold. Hurry up.

949
00:35:42,060 --> 00:35:43,800
- Buy whatever you want.
- Go back quickly.

950
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,020
All right? Treat yourself well.

951
00:35:45,020 --> 00:35:46,460
Call me when you arrive.

952
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:47,020
Sure.

953
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:47,750
Safe journey.

954
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:48,880
- Bye.
- Don't worry.

955
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:49,500
Bye.

956
00:35:49,980 --> 00:35:50,710
I'll call you.

957
00:35:59,790 --> 00:36:00,870
Come back triumphantly!

958
00:36:02,540 --> 00:36:03,950
It's just half a month.

959
00:36:04,270 --> 00:36:05,830
Is he going to miss you that much?

960
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:09,140
That's the way he is.

961
00:36:20,790 --> 00:36:22,230
Where is it?

962
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:25,310
The third car left of you.

963
00:36:27,180 --> 00:36:29,270
Don't look. You'll be found out.

964
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:32,500
The SUV over there. See that?

965
00:36:33,430 --> 00:36:34,180
The silver one?

966
00:36:34,180 --> 00:36:35,460
Yes. That's the one.

967
00:36:35,790 --> 00:36:37,350
Are there two guys inside?

968
00:36:37,830 --> 00:36:39,310
It was them yesterday.

969
00:36:40,620 --> 00:36:41,540
Tomorrow,

970
00:36:41,950 --> 00:36:43,950
when Mr. Hong's statement is released,

971
00:36:44,620 --> 00:36:46,230
we don't have to say anything.

972
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,390
This picture is the best response.

973
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:50,230
That day,

974
00:36:50,390 --> 00:36:52,430
I did leave with Lin Chenxing

975
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:54,350
but I only took his car

976
00:36:54,830 --> 00:36:56,140
to find you.

977
00:36:56,750 --> 00:36:58,390
Don't you have a unit in that building?

978
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,830
As expected of you, Dai.

979
00:37:01,870 --> 00:37:02,830
You are really smart.

980
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,270
However, I think

981
00:37:04,270 --> 00:37:06,230
I still need to say something.

982
00:37:07,350 --> 00:37:08,710
I should also release a statement.

983
00:37:09,580 --> 00:37:10,390
No.

984
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:11,660
Stop it.

985
00:37:11,660 --> 00:37:13,140
It's already a huge enough mess.

986
00:37:14,350 --> 00:37:14,980
No.

987
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:16,430
What if those silly fans

988
00:37:16,430 --> 00:37:17,910
call you a fickle woman?

989
00:37:19,830 --> 00:37:22,180
I must speak for you.

990
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:23,580
I'll just say

991
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:25,430
that we are engaged.

992
00:37:25,980 --> 00:37:26,790
No.

993
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:29,100
You are such a drama king.

994
00:37:29,100 --> 00:37:30,620
I'll wait for the director's signal.

995
00:37:30,870 --> 00:37:31,620
Sure.

996
00:37:33,140 --> 00:37:33,980
Action.

997
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:40,790
Let's go.

998
00:38:12,910 --> 00:38:14,140
Sorry, Mr. Zhang.

999
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:15,980
I got you involved

1000
00:38:15,980 --> 00:38:17,620
because of my mistake.

1001
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:18,390
No.

1002
00:38:19,020 --> 00:38:20,790
You didn't do anything wrong.

1003
00:38:20,790 --> 00:38:22,180
I did.

1004
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:24,830
I should never have agreed to
Lin Chenxing in this movie.

1005
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:27,500
I will never realise

1006
00:38:28,460 --> 00:38:31,230
that I can only choose one
between love and work.

1007
00:38:32,390 --> 00:38:33,710
Tell me. Is this

1008
00:38:33,710 --> 00:38:36,950
love or work?

1009
00:38:37,910 --> 00:38:39,950
This is fake. We are acting.

1010
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:42,060
I think

1011
00:38:45,140 --> 00:38:46,390
we can also be a real thing.

1012
00:38:48,270 --> 00:38:48,950
Dai.

1013
00:38:49,180 --> 00:38:49,980
Well...

1014
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,830
You've been with me for so many years.

1015
00:38:52,830 --> 00:38:53,620
Actually,

1016
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:56,950
I've wanted to
be in a relationship with you.

1017
00:39:00,830 --> 00:39:01,620
No.

1018
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,180
The paparazzi are taking pictures.

1019
00:39:06,270 --> 00:39:07,580
We should give them a scoop.

1020
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:11,660
Are you crazy?

1021
00:39:11,660 --> 00:39:13,230
We can just cheat for the camera.

1022
00:39:13,350 --> 00:39:15,540
No one does cheating like this.

1023
00:39:15,540 --> 00:39:17,540
You'll be exposed if you stand there.

1024
00:39:17,540 --> 00:39:18,790
What should I do? Tell me.

1025
00:39:18,790 --> 00:39:19,540
Do this.

1026
00:39:19,540 --> 00:39:20,870
Sure. What next?

1027
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:22,660
Tilt your head to the side.

1028
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:24,100
Move your head sometimes.

1029
00:39:24,460 --> 00:39:25,140
Just like this?

1030
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:27,240
Your hand doesn't work like this.

1031
00:39:27,240 --> 00:39:29,020
Zhang, your hands
are in the wrong position.

1032
00:39:29,020 --> 00:39:30,750
Haven't you
been in a relationship before?

1033
00:39:30,750 --> 00:39:32,120
Can't you be a little more natural?

1034
00:39:32,980 --> 00:39:34,350
Move a little.

1035
00:39:58,870 --> 00:39:59,540
Cut.

1036
00:40:00,870 --> 00:40:01,620
Lin Chenxing!

1037
00:40:02,710 --> 00:40:04,020
Ms. Dai.

1038
00:40:04,390 --> 00:40:04,750
Mr. Hong.

1039
00:40:04,750 --> 00:40:05,920
I must have kept you waiting.

1040
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:06,790
It's fine.

1041
00:40:06,980 --> 00:40:09,960
I'm so sorry.
Chenxing caught a cold suddenly.

1042
00:40:10,040 --> 00:40:11,440
I'm sure he has caused you trouble.

1043
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:14,180
It's all right. I can understand.
Chenxing's health is more important.

1044
00:40:14,180 --> 00:40:15,660
Tell him to take good care of himself.

1045
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:18,100
Look how tired you are.
You've lost so much weight recently.

1046
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:19,160
You've lost weight as well.

1047
00:40:19,160 --> 00:40:19,980
I'll treat you later.

1048
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:20,750
No problem.

1049
00:40:20,750 --> 00:40:21,430
Let's go. Bye.

1050
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:22,160
Come and visit us.

1051
00:40:23,060 --> 00:40:23,500
Let's go.

1052
00:40:23,500 --> 00:40:24,270
Seriously?

1053
00:40:25,230 --> 00:40:25,980
Ms. Dai.

1054
00:40:26,460 --> 00:40:27,950
It's over just like that?

1055
00:40:27,950 --> 00:40:28,500
Yes.

1056
00:40:29,620 --> 00:40:30,830
But he cheated.

1057
00:40:32,350 --> 00:40:33,460
It's just a small incident.

1058
00:40:33,460 --> 00:40:34,180
It's all over now.

1059
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:36,620
It was a small incident indeed.

1060
00:40:36,620 --> 00:40:38,350
However, you dealt with it in 24 hours.

1061
00:40:38,390 --> 00:40:39,950
You are indeed Ms. Daji.

1062
00:40:41,629 --> 00:40:42,629
If this project

1063
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,020
can resume,

1064
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:44,980
nothing else matters.

1065
00:40:45,430 --> 00:40:47,140
Are you just going to forgive him?

1066
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:49,270
That won't do.

1067
00:40:49,270 --> 00:40:50,830
I'm still feeling angry about it.

1068
00:40:51,350 --> 00:40:52,980
Why should we clean up

1069
00:40:52,980 --> 00:40:54,500
the mess he caused?

1070
00:40:55,540 --> 00:40:56,950
This won't do.

1071
00:40:57,060 --> 00:40:58,230
I'm angry.

1072
00:40:59,540 --> 00:41:00,390
You're angry, right?

1073
00:41:08,870 --> 00:41:09,660
What do you think?

1074
00:41:10,580 --> 00:41:11,500
Do you feel better now?

1075
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:14,720
I'll only feel better
if I wreck them all.

1076
00:41:15,710 --> 00:41:16,180
Here you go.

1077
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:36,620
Pervert! Rubbish!

1078
00:41:36,620 --> 00:41:37,710
How dare you molest me?

1079
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:39,100
Do you know I can fight?

1080
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:44,230
Fine. I quit.

1081
00:41:44,790 --> 00:41:45,620
What did you say?

1082
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:47,640
I said I'm quitting.
I'm terminating my contract.

1083
00:41:47,660 --> 00:41:49,430
I have the right to choose, right?

1084
00:41:51,540 --> 00:41:52,880
I'm going to divorce your father.

1085
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:54,910
You must be on my side this time.

1086
00:41:56,460 --> 00:41:57,750
Both of you disgust me.

1087
00:42:16,230 --> 00:42:18,910
I'm officially informing you

1088
00:42:19,100 --> 00:42:21,270
that I am resigning! I quit!

1089
00:42:23,950 --> 00:42:24,760
You're rich, so what?

1090
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,360
What's the use
of having such a big house?

1091
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:27,540
I'm still looking down on you.

1092
00:42:31,580 --> 00:42:32,980
Shichahai!

1093
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:36,460
You're really so small!

1094
00:42:37,540 --> 00:42:39,910
You are not an ocean at all!

1095
00:42:42,580 --> 00:42:44,750
I want to become someone
who shines brightly!

1096
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:05,920
How do you feel? Are you still angry?

1097
00:43:06,460 --> 00:43:07,060
It feels great!

1098
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:36,180
Is it worth it?

1099
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:40,190
From having nothing to having nothing

1100
00:43:41,770 --> 00:43:43,270
Is it worth it?

1101
00:43:43,660 --> 00:43:47,510
To turn back at every crossroads

1102
00:43:49,070 --> 00:43:50,120
Is it worth it?

1103
00:43:50,690 --> 00:43:54,480
Swearing to become the sea,
not just a river

1104
00:43:55,930 --> 00:43:57,350
Is it worth it?

1105
00:43:57,830 --> 00:44:01,940
That night,
the wine was finished with just one sip

1106
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:04,650
Do you dare?

1107
00:44:04,810 --> 00:44:08,600
When having nothing, I don't frown

1108
00:44:10,130 --> 00:44:11,640
Do you dare?

1109
00:44:11,720 --> 00:44:15,990
Once I decide to start,
I hold your hand tightly

1110
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,920
Do you dare?

1111
00:44:18,990 --> 00:44:22,530
Even in the coldest winter,
we feel it on the ice

1112
00:44:24,190 --> 00:44:25,860
Do you dare?

1113
00:44:25,960 --> 00:44:30,090
Striving for an outlet
in reality and love

1114
00:44:31,450 --> 00:44:36,680
Only to realize when we drift apart

1115
00:44:36,760 --> 00:44:41,720
We mistook that day for forever

1116
00:44:41,950 --> 00:44:45,590
Time passes, bidding farewell to youth

1117
00:44:45,620 --> 00:44:50,720
Luckily, we have been brave
ever since we met

1118
00:44:50,900 --> 00:44:56,120
Perhaps that day means forever

1119
00:44:56,640 --> 00:45:01,590
Outrunning time,
leaving the past behind

1120
00:45:04,090 --> 00:45:07,590
Is it worth it?

